Goal: Do not hardcode pam_fail_delay and let pam_unix do its
      job to set a delay...or not

Fixes: #87648

Status wrt upstream: Forwarded but not applied yet

Note: If removed, FAIL_DELAY must be re-added to /etc/login.defs

